    <p>
      <strong>Fuel Injection (FI):</strong> For years we’ve suggested carb motors to keep it simple, however, GM has the bugs worked out and we are ready when you are. Four OEM systems are available, throttle body injection (TBI) that uses a carb looking unit with two centrally located injectors, tuned port injection (TPI) with an injector at each port, the high revving LT-1, and the completely new Vortec V8 motor. All of these FI systems work great with a JCI Conversion Kit.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class= "col-md-2">
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-10">
